  "instructions": [
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together almond flour, coconut milk, maple syrup, egg, vanilla extract, baking powder, and salt until smooth.",
    "Heat a non-stick skillet or griddle over medium heat.",
    "Using a 1/4 cup measuring cup, scoop the batter onto the skillet.",
